\c 17
\s Jehoshafati mambo waJudha
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehoshafati mwanakomana wake akabata ushe pachigaro chake, akazvisimbisa kundorwa naVaIsraeri.
\v 2 Akaisa varwi mumaguta ese akakombwa aJudha, akaisawo mapoka avarwi panyika yaJudha, napamaguta aEfuremu, akange akundwa naAsa baba vake.
\v 3 Jehovha akava naJehoshafati, nokuti akafamba munzira dzokutanga dzababa vake Dhavhidhi; haana kundobvunza vaBhaari;
\v 4 asi akabvunza Mwari wababa vake, akafamba nemirairo yake asingateveri mabasa aIsraeri.
\v 5 Saka Jehovha akasimbisa ushe paruoko rwake; vaJudha vese vakavigira Jehoshafati zvipo, akava nefuma nokukudzwa zvizhinji.
\v 6 Moyo wake ukashingairira nzira dzaJehovha; uye akabvisawo matunhu akakwirira namatanda avo okunamata nawo pakati paJudha.
\p
\v 7 Uye pagore rechitatu rokubata kwake ushe akatuma machinda ake, vanaBhenihairi, naObhadhiya, naZekariya, naNetaneri, naMikaya, kundodzidzisa mumaguta aJudha;
\v 8 uye pamwe chete navo VaRevhi, vana Shemaya, naNetania, naZebhadhia, naAshaheri, naShemiramoti, naJehonatani, naAdhonia, naTobhiya, naTobhiadhonia, vari VaRevhi; uye pamwe chete navo Erishama naJehoramu, vapristi.
\v 9 Vakanodzidzisa pakati paJudha, vane bhuku yomurairo waJehovha; vakafamba vachipota namaguta ese aJudha, vachidzidzisa pakati pavanhu.
\p
\v 10 Ushe hwese hwenyika dzese dzakange dzakapoteredza Judha, vakavhunduswa naJehovha, vakasarwa naJehoshafati.
\v 11 Vamwe VaFirisitia vakavigira Jehoshafati zvipo, nesirivha yomutero; vaArabhiawo vakamuvigira makwai, makondobwe ane zvuru zvinomwe namazana manomwe, nenhongo dzembudzi dzine zvuru zvinomwe namazana manomwe.
\p
\v 12 Jehoshafati akazova mukuru kwazvo, akavaka pakati paJudha nhare namaguta amatura.
\v 13 Waiva namabasa mazhinji mumaguta aJudha, navarwi, varume vane simba noumhare paJerusarema.
\v 14 Zvino ndiwo mazita avo nedzimba, dzamadzibaba avo: Pakati paJudha, vakuru vezvuru: Adhina mukuru, uye pamwe chete naye varume vane simba noumhare vane zvuru zvina mazana matatu;
\v 15 tevere Jehohanani mukuru, uye pamwe chete naye varume vane zvuru zvina mazana maviri namakumi masere;
\v 16 tevere Amasia mwanakomana waZikiri, wakazvipa kuna Jehovha nomoyo wake wese; uye pamwe chete naye varume vane simba noumhare vane zvuru pakati.
\v 17 PavaBhenjamini: Eriadha munhu ane simba noumhare, uye pamwe chete naye varume vane zvuru zvina mazana maviri vakange vakabata uta nenhovo;
\v 18 tevere Jehozabhadhi, uye pamwe chete naye varume vane zvuru zvine zana namakumi masere, vakange vakazvigadzirira kurwa.
\v 19 Ndivo vaibatira mambo, vamwe vakange vaiswa namambo mumaguta akakombwa panyika yese yaJudha vasingaverengwi.
